wikipedia_page.main: Commandant Mary Irene Talbot,  (17 February 1922 – 11 May 2012) was a British naval officer who served as Director of the Women's Royal Naval Service from 1973 to 1976.

response: * Mary Talbot, Countess of Northumberland, courtier who married Anne Boleyn's former suitor, Henry Percy
* Mary Talbot, Countess of Shrewsbury (1556–1632), daughter of Bess of Hardwick
* Mary Talbot Herbert, Countess of Pembroke, (c. 1594 – 1649), daughter of the above
* Mary Talbot (WRNS officer) (1922–2012), British naval officer
